:

*Plašiš se da budeš ranjiv.* (You are afraid of being vulnerable.)
*Plašim se kad se rastajemo.* (I'm scared when we part.)
*Plašiš se da ćeš biti napušten.* (You are afraid of being abandoned.)
*Plašila je da će se izgubiti.* (She was scared of getting lost.)
*Plašili smo se da ćemo biti kažnjeni.* (We were afraid of being punished.)